# Environment Variables

{{ project_name }} uses environment variables for configuration. This page documents all available variables.

## Core Variables

| Variable | Required | Default | Description |
|----------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `APP_NAME` | No | `{{ project_name }}` | Application name |
| `APP_ENV` | No | `development` | Environment: `development`, `staging`, `production` |
| `DEBUG` | No | `false` | Enable debug mode |
| `LOG_LEVEL` | No | `info` | Logging level: `debug`, `info`, `warn`, `error` |

{%- if api_tracks in ['python', 'node', 'python+node'] %}

## API Configuration

| Variable | Required | Default | Description |
|----------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `API_HOST` | No | `0.0.0.0` | API server host |
| `API_PORT` | No | `8000` | API server port |
| `API_WORKERS` | No | `1` | Number of worker processes |
| `CORS_ORIGINS` | No | `*` | Allowed CORS origins (comma-separated) |

{%- endif %}

{%- if docusaurus_search_provider == 'algolia' %}

## Algolia Search

| Variable | Required | Default | Description |
|----------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `ALGOLIA_APP_ID` | Yes | - | Algolia application ID |
| `ALGOLIA_API_KEY` | Yes | - | Algolia search-only API key |
| `ALGOLIA_INDEX_NAME` | Yes | `{{ project_slug }}` | Algolia index name |

{%- endif %}

{%- if docusaurus_search_provider == 'typesense' %}

## Typesense Search

| Variable | Required | Default | Description |
|----------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `TYPESENSE_HOST` | Yes | `localhost` | Typesense server host |
| `TYPESENSE_PORT` | No | `8108` | Typesense server port |
| `TYPESENSE_PROTOCOL` | No | `http` | Protocol: `http` or `https` |
| `TYPESENSE_API_KEY` | Yes | - | Typesense search API key |

{%- endif %}

{%- if docusaurus_analytics == 'posthog' %}

## PostHog Analytics

| Variable | Required | Default | Description |
|----------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `POSTHOG_API_KEY` | Yes | - | PostHog project API key |
| `POSTHOG_HOST` | No | `https://us.i.posthog.com` | PostHog instance URL |

{%- endif %}

{%- if docusaurus_analytics == 'google' %}

## Google Analytics

| Variable | Required | Default | Description |
|----------|----------|---------|-------------|
| `GOOGLE_ANALYTICS_ID` | Yes | - | Google Analytics 4 measurement ID |

{%- endif %}

## Example .env File

```bash
# Core
APP_NAME={{ project_name }}
APP_ENV=development
DEBUG=true
LOG_LEVEL=debug

{%- if api_tracks in ['python', 'node', 'python+node'] %}

# API
API_HOST=0.0.0.0
API_PORT=8000
{%- endif %}

{%- if docusaurus_search_provider == 'algolia' %}

# Algolia
ALGOLIA_APP_ID=your_app_id
ALGOLIA_API_KEY=your_search_api_key
ALGOLIA_INDEX_NAME={{ project_slug }}
{%- endif %}

{%- if docusaurus_analytics == 'posthog' %}

# PostHog
POSTHOG_API_KEY=phc_your_key_here
{%- endif %}
```

## Loading Environment Variables

Environment variables are loaded automatically in development. For production:

```bash
# Export variables
export $(cat .env | xargs)

# Or use dotenv
source .env
```
{%- endif -%}
